    "path": "src/server/plan",
    "name": "plan",
    "purpose": "Owns server-side plan runtime orchestration. Plan stores description, run_steps, pending_steps, and expected_result, delegates flat StepDraft conversion to Step::from_draft without reserving numeric step numbers, and exposes run step signatures; PlanHub routes valid drafts, logs and discards invalid drafts, stores PlanRecords, emits StepEvent::Trigger for runnable steps, and supports lookup, listing, completion tracking, and stringify snapshots; PlanStringify renders current runtime plans in the flat step-field shape; and PlanError reports duplicate plans, missing plans, missing steps, and invalid draft conversion failures.",
